    "Name": "Storm Raider",
    "Details": "The Storm Raider STM-R3 carries two weapons; a mace on the right arm and a RAC/2 on the left arm, fed by a single ton of ammunition in the left torso. Equipped with MASC and powered by a 210 XL engine, the Storm Raider could reach speeds of almost 130 km/h in brief bursts, and was protected by seven tons of Lexington Ltd. Medium Grade standard armor with CASE protecting the ammunition.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.15</color></b>",
